This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-platinum layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky.git
  branch: dunfell/hardknott/master

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-platinum layer to the xxxx mailing list (xxxx@zzzz.org)
and cc: the maintainer:

Maintainer: Josef Holzmayr <jester@theyoctojester.info>

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-platinum layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-platinum layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-platinum'

Enable the ptest DISTRO_FEATURE, for example via

DISTRO_FEATURES_append = " ptest"

in local.conf

II. Misc
========

This layer shows a simple ptest-enabled recipe (libanswer) and a corresponding image (platinum-image)
